These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, pepper, eggplant, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, camping, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, scientific, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, rock, funk, folk
4 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, frog, rat
 1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the fan of indie is the person eating peach##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating peach##1
10. the owner of the frog is the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | pepper    | eggplant      | peach  | radish     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | camping   | video-games | dancing      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | action | mystery     | satire    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | rock         | indie  | funk    |
| Pet           | frog      | rat       | pony | goldfish |

