.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, milk, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, western, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, funk, metal, blues
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, baseball, ice-hockey
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the owner of the frog is the fan of blues##1
 9. the person watching western movies is the fan of metal##1
10. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | sprite      | cola     | milk    | juice |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | crime   | western   | comedy           |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | blues     | metal    | classical         |
| Pet           | bird         | frog | guinea-pig     | chinchilla        |
| Sport         | tennis     | ice-hockey  | lacrosse | baseball       |

