.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, orange, tomato, spinach
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, canadian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret, guinea-pig, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, biathlon, rowing
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, boat, helicopter
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 3. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating tomato##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the egyptian is the owner of the ferret##1
10. the argentine is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cucumber    | spinach      | tomato  | orange   |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | canadian      | argentine | malaysian      |
| Pet           | ferret       | hamster         | goldfish  | guinea-pig         |
| Sport         | swimming | volleyball | biathlon  | rowing |
| Transport     | boat       | jet-ski         | helicopter   | scooter        |

