.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, almond-milk, milk
There 4 different types of food: pear, watermelon, banana, apple
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, polish, egyptian, american
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, bird, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, scooter, quad-bike
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the person eating apple is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the american is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating apple is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the person eating pear##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | milk   | 7up      | iced-tea     |
| Food          | banana     | pear   | apple | watermelon |
| Nationality   | polish | egyptian | pakistani   | american       |
| Pet           | goldfish       | rabbit      | chinchilla     | bird |
| Transport     | car    | scooter     | quad-bike     | tram     |

