 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the designer##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the freelancer is on the far left##1
13. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the pakistani is on the right of the brazilian##1

