| Hobby       | camping    | card-games        | photography  | magic-tricks      |
| Job         | writer  | mechanic | musician | entrepreneur |
| Pet         | snake | rabbit          | goat         | frog      |
| Transport   | boat     | bike     | bus       | jet-ski          |

