.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, fanta, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, photography, rock-climbing, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, zombie, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, canadian, australian, polish
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, goat, hedgehog
 1. the australian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the polish is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the italian is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | fanta      | coffee      | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | rock-climbing | photography | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | animation     | comedy      | fantasy |
| Nationality   | australian  | polish     | italian    | canadian  |
| Pet           | goldfish  | hedgehog       | mouse          | goat      |

