.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, banana, kiwi, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, baking, photography, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, drama, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, soccer, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, car, trike
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating banana##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating kiwi##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | grapes      | banana     | papaya        | kiwi     |
| Hobby         | photography     | cooking    | gardening | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | drama  | fantasy      | satire       |
| Sport         | soccer      | tennis | weightlifting     | biathlon        |
| Transport     | car   | trike     | scooter  | boat       |

