.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, pomegranate, papaya, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, baking, cooking, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, project-manager, fisherman, bartender
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, bird, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, airplane, skateboard, van
 1. the bartender is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the bartender is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the journalist##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the project-manager##1
 8. the journalist is the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person eating papaya is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person eating radish is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | pomegranate    | radish        | pineapple        | papaya      |
| Hobby       | cooking       | singing       | baking      | filmmaking |
| Job         | project-manager | bartender | fisherman | journalist      |
| Pet         | dog          | turtle         | chinchilla           | bird    |
| Transport   | skateboard         | airplane       | van     | tram   |

 